          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Use this property to specify how much to debit from the user’s account and apply to the bill payment. Always specify the precise amount to transfer and not just a constant indicating that the user wants to pay the current balance or the minimum due. For example, you might create an "
